      "rendered": "15 Online Job Boards for Nonprofit Professionals"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.gif\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-15258 alignright\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits-300x300.gif?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.gif?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.gif?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.gif?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.gif?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Working at a nonprofit\u00a0often\u00a0pays less than the for-profit sector, but the perks of extended vacation time, flex time, and the personal satisfaction of having a meaningful professional life can outweigh the financial downside of building a nonprofit career. And the good news is that <strong><a href=\"http://www.nonprofithr.com/2015-employment-practices-survey-download/\" target=\"_blank\">2015 is predicted to be a great year for nonprofit sector hiring</a>\u00a0</strong>thanks to a rebounding\u00a0economy. Many nonprofit professionals who have weathered years of pay freezes and minimal advancement are ready for a change. That said, below are 15 resources to help you find your next nonprofit dream job.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1. Aid Jobs (International) <a href=\"http://aidjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\">aidjobs.org</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aidjobs\" target=\"_blank\">@aidjobs</a></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://aidjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15219\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/aid-jobs.png?resize=600%2C382\" alt=\"aid jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/aid-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/aid-jobs.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. The Bridgespan Group<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bridgespan.org/\" target=\"_blank\">bridgespan.org</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bridgespangroup\" target=\"_blank\">@bridgespangroup</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.bridgespan.org/Home.aspx\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15222\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bridgespan-group-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"bridgespan group nonprofit jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bridgespan-group-nonprofit-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bridgespan-group-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Charity Village (Canada)<br />\n<a href=\"http://charityvillage.com/\" target=\"_blank\">charityvillage.com</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/charityvillage\" target=\"_blank\">@charityvillage</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://charityvillage.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15224\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/charity-village-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=600%2C358\" alt=\"charity village nonprofit jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/charity-village-nonprofit-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/charity-village-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Chronicle of Philanthropy<br />\n<a href=\"http://philanthropy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">philanthropy.com</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/philanthropy\" target=\"_blank\">@philanthropy</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.philanthropy.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17539\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Philanthropy.png?resize=600%2C297\" alt=\"Philanthropy\" width=\"600\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Philanthropy.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Philanthropy.png?resize=300%2C148&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Common Good Careers<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cgcareers.org/\" target=\"_blank\">cgcareers.org</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CGCareers\" target=\"_blank\">@CGCareers</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://commongoodcareers.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17541\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Common-Good-Careers.png?resize=600%2C343\" alt=\"Common Good Careers\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Common-Good-Careers.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Common-Good-Careers.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. DevNetJobs.org (International)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.devnetjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\">devnetjobs.org</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/devnetjobs\" target=\"_blank\">@devnetjobs</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.devnetjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15233\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/dev-net-jobs.png?resize=600%2C383\" alt=\"dev net jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/dev-net-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/dev-net-jobs.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Devex (International)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.devex.com\" target=\"_blank\">devex.com</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/devex\" target=\"_blank\">@devex</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.devex.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15235\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/devex-international-development-jobs.png?resize=600%2C342\" alt=\"devex international development jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/devex-international-development-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/devex-international-development-jobs.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Idealist\u00a0<strong>(International)<br />\n</strong><a href=\"http://www.idealist.org/\" target=\"_blank\">idealist.org</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/idealist\" target=\"_blank\">@idealist</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.idealist.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17544\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/IDealist.png?resize=600%2C285\" alt=\"IDealist\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/IDealist.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/IDealist.png?resize=300%2C142&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. NGOJobsOnline.com (International)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ngojobsonline.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ngojobsonline.com</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ngojobsonline\" target=\"_blank\">@ngojobsonline</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.ngojobsonline.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15245\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/ngojobsonline.png?resize=600%2C324\" alt=\"ngojobsonline\" width=\"600\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/ngojobsonline.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/ngojobsonline.png?resize=300%2C162&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. The Nonprofit Times<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thenonprofittimes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">thenonprofittimes.com</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofittimes\" target=\"_blank\">@nonprofittimes</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.thenonprofittimes.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15240\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/nonprofit-times-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=600%2C336\" alt=\"nonprofit times nonprofit jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/nonprofit-times-nonprofit-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/nonprofit-times-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. OpportunityKnocks<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.opportunityknocks.org/\" target=\"_blank\">opportunityknocks.org</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OppKnocksCareer\" target=\"_blank\">@OppKnocksCareer</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.opportunityknocks.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15242\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/OpportunityNocs.png?resize=600%2C356\" alt=\"OpportunityNocs\" width=\"600\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/OpportunityNocs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/OpportunityNocs.png?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">12. Philanthropy News Digest<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.philanthropynewsdigest.org/\" target=\"_blank\">philanthropynewsdigest.org</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/pndblog\" target=\"_blank\">@pndblog</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.philanthropynewsdigest.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15247\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/philanthropy-news-digest-jobs.png?resize=600%2C382\" alt=\"philanthropy news digest jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/philanthropy-news-digest-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/philanthropy-news-digest-jobs.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">13. Pro Bono Australia<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.probonoaustralia.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">probonoaustralia.com.au</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ProBonoNews/\" target=\"_blank\">@probononews</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.probonoaustralia.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15249\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/probono-australia-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=600%2C367\" alt=\"probono australia nonprofit jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/probono-australia-nonprofit-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/probono-australia-nonprofit-jobs.png?resize=300%2C183&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">14. Third Sector Jobs (United Kingdom)<br />\n<a href=\"http://jobs.thirdsector.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">jobs.thirdsector.co.uk</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jobsthirdsector\" target=\"_blank\">@jobsthirdsector</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://jobs.thirdsector.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15252\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/third-sector-jobs.png?resize=600%2C372\" alt=\"third sector jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/third-sector-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/third-sector-jobs.png?resize=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">15. United Nations Jobs (International)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.unjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\">unjobs.org</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UNjobs\" target=\"_blank\">@UNjobs</a><a href=\"http://unjobs.org/\"><br />\n</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://unjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15253\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/UN-Jobs.png?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"UN Jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/UN-Jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/UN-Jobs.png?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
